description:
This First Chapter Meeting will bring together entrepreneurs in the healthcare sector who will showcase their demo during a 4-min presentation, followed by a few minutes of Q&A. After the demo-session, we will do some matchmaking where you can mingle with all the attendees to exchange experiences and get feedback on your demo. RSVP now at the right top of this page!  

For more info go to www.health20belgium.be
name: First Health2.0 Chapter Meeting Brussels
